;;color:#0088CC;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"> </span></u></b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">&ndash;</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:#1F497D;mso-themecolor:text2;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Contact your Network national contact for advice to business with special focus on SMEs. The support includes guidance on EU research funding.</span><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif;color:black\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span><a href=\"http://www.iprhelpdesk.eu/\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;&#10;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;&#10;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">Intellectual Property Helpdesk</span></a> <span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;mso-fareast-font-family:&#10;&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;color:black;mso-fareast-language:EN-GB\">&ndash; Contact the IP Helpdesk for advice on the IP elements of your grant agreement.<o:p></o:p></span></p>", "sepTemplate": "<p>To access the Electronic Submission Service, please click on the submission-button next to the <strong>type of action</strong> and the <strong>type of model grant agreement</strong> that corresponds to your proposal. You will then be asked to confirm your choice, as it cannot be changed in the submission system. Upon confirmation, you will be linked to the correct entry point.</p>\r\n<p>To access existing draft proposals for this topic, please login to the Funding &amp; Tenders Portal and select the My Proposals page of the My Area section.</p>", "links": [], "additionalDossiers": [], "infoPackDossiers": [], "callDetailsJSONItem": {"staticAdditionalInfo": "<p><span style=\"color:#333333;\">Calls for proposals for action grants in 2021 will aim at providing financial contributions to organisations offering assistance to consumers in Member States in the form of debt advice. </span></p><p><span style=\"color:#333333;\">The applicants shall be facilitating the access of consumers to debt advice and to support measures for vulnerable consumers.</span></p><p><span style=\"color:#333333;\">In particular, the following activities should be prioritised: make providers of assistance of debt advice more accessible to consumers, including the improvement of their operational capacity in resolving consumer problems, develop the networking of debt advice entities, promote monitoring activities on the functioning and the effectiveness of debt advice mechanisms.</span></p><p><span style=\"color:#333333;\">The maximum co-financing rate for grants covered under this call is 95%.</span></p>\n", "latestInfos": [{"approvalDate": "Jun 22, 2021 3:46:39 PM", "lastChangeDate": "Jun 22, 2021 3:46:39 PM", "content": "The submission session is now available for: SMP-CONS-2021-DA(SMP-PJG)"}], "hasForthcomingTopics": false, "hasOpenTopics": false, "allClosedTopics": true}}}